Author: Aleph0-4
Text: I'm not gonna tell you that you're not disgusting because you probably wouldn't believe me. But please try to be compassionate: your body is incredibly resilient. You've given it hate and abuse but it still continues to work for you. People who are shitty will only think it's easier to break you when you're 'small enough'.
